                    <p class="text-white/80 font-normal">Ing Heng approved in 18 hours with 10% deposit.</p>
                    <p class="text-green-500/60 font-normal underline decoration-1 underline-offset-4">Result: Project completed, RM 250k profit, fleet expanded to 3 machines.</p>
